result.execSummary:
The defendant Jesu S Gonzalez was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. On one or more other charges, Jesu S Gonzalez was found not guilty. These charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Jesu S Gonzalez is presumed innocent of the not guilty charges.

  • Jesu S Gonzalez was found guilty of 2nd-Degree Recklessly Endangering Safety, a class G felony, Wisconsin Statutes 941.30(2).
  • Jesu S Gonzalez was found guilty of 2nd-Degree Recklessly Endangering Safety, a class G felony, Wisconsin Statutes 941.30(2).
  • Jesu S Gonzalez was found guilty of Drive or Operate Vehicle w/o Consent, a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 943.23(3).
  • Jesu S Gonzalez was found guilty of Vehicle Operator Flee/Elude Officer, a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 346.04(3).
  • Jesu S Gonzalez was found guilty of Bail Jumping-Felony, a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(b).
